@startuml
title 电商订单超时自动关单流程

actor User
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Message Queue" as MQ
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Timeout Checker" as Checker

User -> Order: 创建订单请求
activate Order
Order -> Inventory: 扣减库存 (锁定库存)
activate Inventory
Inventory --> Order: 库存扣减成功
deactivate Inventory

Order -> Order: 创建订单 (状态: pending)
Order -> MQ: 发送延迟消息 (TTL=30分钟)
note right of MQ: 消息在30分钟后进入死信队列

alt 用户在30分钟内支付成功
    User -> Order: 支付回调
    activate Order
    Order -> Order: 更新订单状态为 paid
    Order -> MQ: 取消对应的延迟消息 (可选)
    deactivate Order
else 30分钟内未支付
    MQ -> Checker: 延迟消息进入死信队列
    activate Checker
    Checker -> Order: 查询超时订单
    activate Order
    Order --> Checker: 返回pending订单
    deactivate Order
    
    Checker -> Order: 关闭订单 (状态: cancelled)
    activate Order
    Order -> Inventory: 回滚库存 (释放锁定库存)
    activate Inventory
    Inventory --> Order: 库存回滚成功
    deactivate Inventory
    
    Order --> Checker: 订单关闭成功
    deactivate Order
    deactivate Checker
end

@enduml